name: Ausmove
overview:
If you are in New Zealand and want to move to Australia then Ausmove is the best pick for you. They are 100% New Zealand owned and operated company, so they will understand your needs perfectly. With over 19 years of experience in shipping/moving households safely to Australia from New Zealand, they take pride and guarantee complete satisfaction to their customers.

The reason why Ausmove have been successful is the way they operate. They help you move household item to Australia with care and right on time, like any individual would do to its own property. So you won’t ever feel that your stuff is in the wrong hands. When goods are shipped to Australia they will be as good as you saw them last.

Since Ausmove believes in customer satisfaction, they provide you with free quote and free advice on how you can ship your items to Australia with care. Size doesn’t matter. Ship your car, motorcycle or just anything, they will arrange safe and secured car shipping to Australia.
